| Command              | Simple Meaning        |
| -------------------- | --------------------- |
| `pwd`                | Show current location |
| `ls`                 | Show files/folders    |
| `cd folder`          | Enter folder          |
| `cd ..`              | Go back               |
| `clear`              | Clear screen          |
| `mkdir name`         | Create folder         |
| `touch file.txt`     | Create file           |
| `cat file.txt`       | Read file             |
| `nano file.txt`      | Edit file             |
| `cp a b`             | Copy file             |
| `mv a b`             | Move/Rename file      |
| `rm file.txt`        | Delete file           |
| `rm -r folder`       | Delete folder         |
| `echo hello`         | Print text                 |
| `grep word file.txt` | Search word in file   |
| `find . -name file`  | Find file             |
| `sudo command`       | Run as admin          |
| `whoami`             | Show username         |
| `history`            | Show old commands     |
| `top`                | Show system usage     |
| `ps`                 | Show running programs |
| `kill PID`           | Stop program          |
| `df -h`              | Show storage          |
| `free -h`            | Show RAM              |
| `ping google.com`    | Check internet        |
| `wget url`           | Download file         |
| `man ls`             | Help/manual           |
| `exit`               | Close terminal        |
